claim.claim-text:
1. A micromechanical component comprising: 
a substrate; 
at least one structured layer on the substrate, wherein at least one functional structure is formed in the at least one structured layer; 
a cap covering the functional structure, wherein at least one cavity is formed between the cap and the at least one functional structure; and 
a connecting layer to connect the cap with the structured layer, wherein the connecting layer is formed by an anodically bondable glass having a thickness in a range of 300 nm to 100 &mgr;m.
